or something, so...

174
00:13:51,164 --> 00:13:57,952
I went into her room,
and that's when I found her.

175
00:13:58,046 --> 00:14:00,454
I saw her on the floor

176
00:14:00,549 --> 00:14:06,594
and I thought
I could help her, but...

177
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:11,299
