I don't have any relatives.

210
00:15:40,649 --> 00:15:42,774
-None at all?
-My mom has a cousin,

211
00:15:42,859 --> 00:15:45,726
Sarah-Louise, but...

212
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:47,362
