and I hardly know her.

214
00:15:50,408 --> 00:15:53,660
Do you have her number?

215
00:15:53,745 --> 00:15:54,786
No.

216
00:15:54,871 --> 00:15:56,079
Okay.

217
00:15:56,206 --> 00:15:57,914
